### Changelog Writing Rules

```markdown
âœ… DO:
- Write user-facing changes (not internals)
- Link to relevant issues/PRs
- Group by type (Added, Changed, Fixed, etc.)
- Keep descriptions concise

âŒ DON'T:
- Include "version 2.0.0 released" entries
- Merge multiple versions into one
- Write internal refactor notes
- Use vague language
```

