## âš ï¸ Anti-Patterns

| âŒ NEVER | âœ… ALWAYS | Why |
|---------|-----------|-----|
| "Coming soon" placeholders | Complete documentation or TODO issues | Users need info now |
| Outdated examples | Tested, working examples | Frustrating when code doesn't work |
| Walls of text | Structured with headers, lists, code | Scannability |
| Assuming knowledge | Context and prerequisites | Clearer onboarding |
| Writing code without comments | Self-documenting code + key comments | Maintainability |
| Not updating docs | Docs synced with code changes | Accuracy |
| Jargon without explanation | Plain language + technical terms | Accessibility |

